   &'static str }` shape at `fathomdb-schema/src/lib.rs:51-54`
   (re-verified) — pure SQL, no Rust callback extension point.
   CASE WHEN is the migration-time mirror of the D3 helper
   `resolve_source_type`; P1-IMPL is directed to add a
